{
  "stem": "25423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I returned with the priest from the Polish end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's the way I crossed the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from then on, I tried to become myself again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kurt Lewin.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For only three weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I realized that there are pogroms, Jews are being killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And although the Germans are gone, the Poles are still creating a danger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I shifted to a Polish name and that's it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Roman Matkowski.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I fabricated them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to think like Roman Mytka.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, I wouldn't survive or I would go mad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Equally so, I served in the Polish army as Roman Matkowski, so I had to think like Roman Matkowski.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to suppress and just put things in a little corner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was an infantry man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was a second lieutenant because I knew how to read and write.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after the war, for a short while, I was sort of a head of a office, you know, clerk, senior clerk.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you see, the same-- the question which you ask is the same, which faces me today.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In order to communicate, with my present environment, I cannot revert either to my life as a monk, or my life in the ghetto, or life in the Polish army, or, for that matter, life in this era.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this is a corner, you see which--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite a number of people because I make friends very easily, and some survivors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From September or October 1944 until May, June, until August 1945.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I demobilized because, you see, having served during the war in combat, I was entitled to be demobilized immediately when the war ended or shortly afterwards.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I picked up two Catholic priests Father Marek and another one, and we ran away from Poland to Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
